modName: Daedric Space Armor a standalone retexture
summary: This mod adds a standalone retexture of the original daedric armor with a sci fi space age look to it.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a standalone retexture of the original daedric armor with a sci fi space age look to it. You can find the armor outside of the Crabber\'s Shanty.

Stats:
chest: 56 armor
helm: 25 armor
gauntlets: 21 armor
boots: 21 armor
Temperable: yes

Future Changes: Never, I\'m done with the creation engine and all of its god awful bugs. Free at last!
author: Sorrien
